[4] Pakistan (Ghotki)
Date: Mon 30 Apr 2018. 7:35 PM
Source: Urdu Point [edited]
https://www.urdupoint.com/en/pakistan/five-children-die-several-affected-of-measle-332162.html


At least 5 children died and dozens others fell seriously sick due to a measles outbreak in various areas of Ghotki. Sources said that the epidemic measles went uncontrolled due to lack of interest of the authorities concerned.

The negligence resulted in death of 5 children hailing from various areas in a couple of days while dozens others were affected and hospitalized.

[Byline: Mohammad Ali]

